---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title='Plasterers & Painters in Denham | Hancock' description='Plastering and painting in Denham. Fixed-price quotes from City & Guilds certified contractors covering Denham and the surrounding area.' activePage='areas'>
<section style="position:relative;height:360px;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;">
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background-image:url('/uploads/Hancock-plastering-and-painting%20(3).webp');background-size:cover;background-position:center 45%;"></div>
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(15,23,42,0.9) 0%,rgba(15,23,42,0.45) 60%,rgba(15,23,42,0.15) 100%);"></div>
  <div style="position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px 48px;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;">
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);margin:0 0 12px;"><a href="/" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Home</a> / <a href="/areas" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Areas</a> / Denham</p>
    <h1 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(34px,5vw,56px);font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;margin:0 0 12px;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:1.05;">Plasterer in Denham</h1>
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:17px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75);margin:0;">UB9/SL9 · Plastering &amp; painting for Denham's village properties and executive homes.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:56px 24px;background:#ffffff;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;gap:48px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
    <div style="flex:2;min-width:260px;">
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">About this area</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,30px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 18px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">An affluent village on our doorstep. Period properties and executive homes in the Green Belt.</h2>
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 14px;">Denham is a commuter village straddling the UB9/SL9 postcode boundary — a short distance from Harefield. The village itself has period cottages, farmhouses, and an Edwardian character in its conservation area streets. The surrounding land holds newer executive homes on larger plots.</p>
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">Denham generates demand for high-end finishes — Venetian plastering, quality exterior paint systems, and sash window painting on the period properties. The executive homes on the edge of the village tend to want skimming and decorating during renovation programmes.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="flex:1;min-width:200px;">
      <div style="background:#F8FAFC;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:8px;padding:20px;">
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:#64748B;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;margin:0 0 14px;">Quick facts</p>
        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:9px;">
          <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;padding-bottom:9px;"><span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#64748B;">Postcode</span><span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;">UB9 / SL9</span></div>
          <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;padding-bottom:9px;"><span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#64748B;">Character</span><span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;">Village / executive</span></div>
          <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;"><span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#64748B;">From Harefield</span><span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;">~8 mins</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:56px 24px;background:#F8FAFC;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;gap:64px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
    <div style="flex:1;min-width:300px;">
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">Neighbourhoods we work in</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,30px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 18px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">From the old village to Higher Denham.</h2>
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 14px;">Denham splits into distinct pockets. <strong>Denham Village</strong> — around Village Road and the Misbourne — is a genuine conservation-area settlement of period cottages, farmhouses, and the famous former film studios, with solid-brick and lime-plaster construction that needs sympathetic handling. <strong>Denham Green</strong> and the roads toward the A40 bring 20th-century and executive housing, while <strong>Higher Denham</strong> is a quieter, semi-rural enclave of detached homes on generous plots.</p>
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">The Green Belt setting and the proximity of the Colne and Misbourne rivers mean some lower-lying properties carry a higher damp exposure — relevant when diagnosing plaster failure on the older village stock.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="flex:1;min-width:300px;">
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">What homeowners ask for</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,30px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 18px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">High-end finishes and period repair.</h2>
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 14px;">Denham is an affluent, considered market. The period properties drive Venetian plastering, lime-compatible repair, and sash window overhaul and painting; the executive homes bring skimming, ceiling work, and quality interior decorating during renovation. Exterior render and masonry paint systems on the larger houses we schedule for the drier months so the finish cures properly.</p>
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">Clients here expect a high standard and a clear, fixed price agreed before we start — which is exactly how we quote every Denham job.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:56px 24px;background:#ffffff;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 24px;">Working in Denham</p>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:20px;">
      <div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">~8 minutes from base</h3>
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Denham is effectively next door to Harefield — one of our closest areas. No travel cost, easy scheduling, and we can usually take a look quickly.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Period-aware</h3>
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">The village conservation stock needs breathable, period-appropriate materials. We assess the wall before specifying — modern gypsum isn't always the right call.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Access &amp; parking</h3>
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Executive plots have ample space; the narrow village lanes we plan loading around. Either way, no disruption to you or your neighbours.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Clean, tidy, insured</h3>
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Surfaces protected, site left immaculate. Fully insured, City &amp; Guilds qualified, no subcontractors.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:0;">
  <div style="position:relative;height:clamp(300px,42vw,440px);">
    <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:url('/uploads/Hancock-plastering-and-painting%20(6)%20.webp');background-size:cover;background-position:center;"></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(15,23,42,0.78) 0%,rgba(15,23,42,0.18) 55%,rgba(15,23,42,0) 100%);"></div>
    <div style="position:relative;max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;height:100%;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;padding:0 24px 40px;box-sizing:border-box;">
      <p style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(18px,2.4vw,26px);font-weight:600;color:#ffffff;max-width:600px;margin:0;letter-spacing:-0.02em;line-height:1.3;">Polished Venetian plaster, applied by hand to a flawless finish.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
