</section>
<section style="padding:56px 24px;background:#0F172A;">
  <div style="max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;">
    <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(24px,4vw,38px);font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;margin:0 0 14px;letter-spacing:-0.04em;">Get a quote for work in Denham.</h2>
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);margin:0 0 32px;">Fixed price. Based in nearby Harefield UB9.</p>
