      <a href="/contact" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;background:#0C7BA8;color:#ffffff;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;padding:14px 28px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;">Get a Free Quote</a>
